# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CircleCore — Billing Environment Variables
# CC-17 FIX: This file was previously zero bytes. All required billing keys
# are now documented here.
#
# USAGE:
#   Copy the relevant keys into your .env file and replace placeholder values
#   with real credentials from your Stripe and Razorpay dashboards.
#
# STRIPE KEYS:
#   https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys
#   https://dashboard.stripe.com/webhooks
#   https://dashboard.stripe.com/products  (for Price IDs)
#
# RAZORPAY KEYS:
#   https://dashboard.razorpay.com/app/keys
#   https://dashboard.razorpay.com/app/webhooks
#   https://dashboard.razorpay.com/app/subscriptions/plans  (for Plan IDs)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ─── Stripe ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Secret key — NEVER expose this on the frontend
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...

# Webhook signing secret — from Stripe Dashboard → Webhooks → your endpoint
# Used to verify that webhook events actually come from Stripe (HMAC verification)
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...

# Stripe Price IDs — create products at https://dashboard.stripe.com/products
# Each price represents one billing interval for one tier
STRIPE_PREMIUM_MONTHLY_PRICE_ID=price_...
STRIPE_PREMIUM_ANNUAL_PRICE_ID=price_...
STRIPE_ENTERPRISE_MONTHLY_PRICE_ID=price_...
STRIPE_ENTERPRISE_ANNUAL_PRICE_ID=price_...

# ─── Razorpay ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# API credentials — from Razorpay Dashboard → Settings → API Keys
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=rzp_test_...
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=...

# Webhook secret — from Razorpay Dashboard → Webhooks → your endpoint
# Used for HMAC signature verification on incoming webhook events
RAZORPAY_WEBHOOK_SECRET=...

# Razorpay Plan IDs — create subscription plans at:
# https://dashboard.razorpay.com/app/subscriptions/plans
RAZORPAY_PREMIUM_MONTHLY_PLAN_ID=plan_...
RAZORPAY_PREMIUM_ANNUAL_PLAN_ID=plan_...
RAZORPAY_ENTERPRISE_MONTHLY_PLAN_ID=plan_...
RAZORPAY_ENTERPRISE_ANNUAL_PLAN_ID=plan_...
